The Governor of Adamawa State, Rt Hon Ahmadu Umaru Fintiri has congratulated his counterpart, the Governor of Taraba State, His Excellency Arch Ishaku Darius over the victory at the apex court on Wednesday afternoon. In a statement signed by Humwashi Wonosikou, his Press Secretary, Ahmadu said Darius Ishaku deserved the victory given his widespread acceptance across the state. ALSO READ: South-West governors launch Amotekun PDP hails Supreme Court’s ruling on Abia, Delta,… Supreme Court upholds Okowa, Bello, Ishaku, Ikpeazu… Oboro congratulates Okowa on victory at Supreme Court Adamawa gov condemns resurgence of Boko Haram attacks He said the Wednesday’s judgement of the Supreme Court affirming his electoral victory has further demonstrated that his election was indeed a true reflection of the wishes of the people of Taraba State. Fintiri advised Governor Darius to extend a hand of fellowship to the opposition in Taraba State and dedicate himself to re-uniting the people and be the governor to all. He said: “The path is now clear for focus piloting of the state’s affairs towards lifting Taraba higher in his last term as governor, etching his name in gold as one who changed the negative narrative of Taraba.” STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO  WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS FREE PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE